; Hdr:L64002
;
; Header file for LSI Logic L64002 MPEG 2 audio/video decoder chip
; Must get Hdr:MPEG2Card first

; ***********************************
; ***    C h a n g e   L i s t    ***
; ***********************************

; Date       Who  Version       Description
; ----       ---  -------       -----------
; 25-Apr-95  TMD  -		Created
